{"id":232967273,"title":"Kobe與女兒GiGi墜機去世","content":"我只希望明天的新聞是\n一身髒兮兮的老科牽著GiGi從森林走了出來\n我還在等kobe培養GiGi\nGiGi跟Bronny在一起 \n據報導 Kobe 最後一刻試圖向地面拋下GiGi\n這是他凌晨四點最後的執著。\n\n更—\n昨天半夜知道消息後 原Po我抱著我的球鞋哭的很慘\n直接拿到床上抱著 他是我的信仰 我的光\n昨天看到GIGI的後仰 跟爸爸一模一樣 \n心中充滿 驕傲 難過 心疼 遺憾\n我只能想到當時GIGI很害怕\n老大他是拼了命的想保護GIGI\n洛杉磯的四點一直停留 噓 老大要起床訓練了...\nKobe四點起來訓練 Kobe死於四點的空難\n拜託有些人尊重死者 你可以不喜歡 那就別評論了\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d855def-d005-4e8b-a0a1-1fca259246ee/full.jpeg","excerpt":"我只希望明天的新聞是，一身髒兮兮的老科牽著GiGi從森林走了出來，我還在等kobe培養GiGi，GiGi跟Bronny在一起，據報導 Kobe 最後一刻試圖向地面拋下GiGi，這是他凌晨四點最後的執著","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"863b960a-72a8-4479-80a2-b976275c002e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T12:55:29.434Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-28T12:27:54.746Z","commentCount":22,"likeCount":575,"tags":[],"topics":["NBA","籃球","墜機","KobeBryant"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"籃球","forumAlias":"basketball","school":"國立臺灣大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":520},{"id":"514c2569-fd53-4d9d-a415-bf0f88e7329f","count":51},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":2},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d855def-d005-4e8b-a0a1-1fca259246ee/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"9bb39f53-9163-458e-841e-be94a793692b","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d855def-d005-4e8b-a0a1-1fca259246ee/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d855def-d005-4e8b-a0a1-1fca259246ee/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7d855def-d005-4e8b-a0a1-1fca259246ee/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T12: